    <item>
      <title>审计师表示，瑞典 Alecta 高管不对失误负责</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/sweden-s-alecta-executives-not-liable-for-missteps-auditor-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位审计师表示，瑞典最大养老基金 Alecta 的董事会成员和首席执行官不应为导致 2023 年投资失败损失 31 亿美元的决策承担个人责任。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/sweden-s-alecta-executives-not-liable-for-missteps-auditor-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 09:07:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马来西亚拒绝主办英联邦运动会，理由是成本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/malaysia-declines-offer-to-host-commonwealth-games-cites-costs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚紧随澳大利亚之后，因成本问题而拒绝主办 2026 年英联邦运动会，因为距离运动会开幕仅剩两年，组织者仍在继续寻找新的主办国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/malaysia-declines-offer-to-host-commonwealth-games-cites-costs</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 09:01:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度停止接收通过Sovcomflot油轮交付的俄罗斯石油</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/india-stops-taking-russian-oil-delivered-on-sovcomflot-tankers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国的制裁，所有印度炼油厂现在都拒绝接收 PJSC Sovcomflot 油轮上运载的俄罗斯原油，这使得自两年前入侵乌克兰以来蓬勃发展的贸易进一步复杂化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/india-stops-taking-russian-oil-delivered-on-sovcomflot-tankers</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 08:53:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
