      <title>西班牙监管机构表示 Grifols 的财务状况没有重大错误</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/grifols-financials-have-no-big-errors-spanish-regulator-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙证券监管机构表示，他们没有发现 Grifols SA 的财务报告存在任何重大错误，尽管这家制药公司的某些数据确实存在一些缺陷。股价上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/grifols-financials-have-no-big-errors-spanish-regulator-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 21:06:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟将对俄罗斯谷物征收惩罚性关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/eu-is-poised-to-impose-punitive-tariffs-on-russian-grain</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位欧盟高级官员表示，欧盟执行机构已提议对部分俄罗斯农产品进口征收惩罚性关税，以阻止资金流动并遏制该国战时收入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/eu-is-poised-to-impose-punitive-tariffs-on-russian-grain</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 19:46:43 GMT</pubDate>
